  <course-outcomes>
    <outcome>Understanding of the RFP/RFQ process.</outcome>
    <outcome>Gain a comprehensive understanding of the systems development process </outcome>
    <outcome>Work effectively on teams to develop large systems.  </outcome>
    <outcome>Understand the engineering process and its effect on business </outcome>
    <outcome> Develop a comprehensive systems architecture and engineering document.</outcome>
    <outcome></outcome>
